	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Venerande pater, cum a nobis discessurus esset tabellarius, subito has exaravi et quas landgravio scripseram, celeriter exscribi iussi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Excusabis, si placet, festinationem.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Chronica <persName type="auto_name">Godefredi Viterbensis</persName> accepi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque, si <persName type="auto_name">Hunibaldum</persName> de rebus Francorum habes et <persName type="auto_name">Mamertinum</persName> et <persName type="auto_name">Iacobum de Voragine</persName>, te rogo, ut quam primum mittas, sicuti superioribus literis abs te petieram.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale, venerande pater, et salve.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName type="auto_name">Gvaltero</persName>  S. P., cui, si placet, inclusam chartulam ostendas, ut, si vobis videatur, d. <persName type="auto_name">Stettano</persName> postea mittatur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="auto_name">Genevę</placeName> 20. aprilis, quo die nibus<note type="margin">a.R.: nivibus?</note> agri nostri cooperti magnum nobis luctum afferebant<note type="margin">a.R.: affecerunt?</note></s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dignitatis tuae studiosissimus <persName type="auto_name">Hotomanus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Venerando et clarissimo viro d. Henrico Bullingero, Tigurinae ecclesiae pastori fidelissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Zus' mit <persName>Beza</persName> an HB (21. april 1573) übersandt. Vgl. HB an Egli, 27. april 1573.]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
